+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>

+        android:text="+" />

+    <Button

+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"

+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"

+        android:layout_alignBottom="@+id/btn0"

+        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/btn9"
+        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/btn9" />

+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="="

+        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/btnCE"
+        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/btnCE" />

+    <Button
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="Backspace"
+        android:id="@+id/btnBackspace"
+        android:layout_above="@+id/btn2"
+        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
+        android:layout_toStartOf="@+id/btn3"
+        android:layout_toLeftOf="@+id/btn3" />
+
+    <Button
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="CE"
+        android:id="@+id/btnCE"
+        android:layout_alignTop="@+id/btnBackspace"
+        android:layout_alignRight="@+id/btnDiv"
+        android:layout_alignEnd="@+id/btnDiv"
+        android:layout_toEndOf="@+id/btn2"
+        android:layout_toRightOf="@+id/btn2" />
+    </RelativeLayout>
+</android.support.design.widget.CoordinatorLayout>
